      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Picture caption with June 8 Making Books column about leading authors and sales shortfall of their recent novels, misidentified book that made one-week appearance on New York Times best-seller list; it was Ravelstein by Saul Bellow, not The Human Stain by Philip Roth</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>A picture caption with the Making Books column yesterday, about leading authors and the sales shortfall of their recent novels, misidentified the work that made a one-week appearance on the New York Times best-seller list. As the article noted, it was ''Ravelstein,'' by Saul Bellow, not ''The Human Stain'' by Philip Roth.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
